00:27:56.338 --> 00:27:57.457
que es tu problema?

00:27:57.858 --> 00:27:58.898
Sí, Banxia.

00:27:59.217 --> 00:28:00.064
Piénsalo.

00:28:15.497 --> 00:28:16.418
Sr. Shen.

