Descansa un poco.

00:35:35.298 --> 00:35:36.192
Cuida, señora.

00:35:42.017 --> 00:35:42.944
Madre.

00:35:46.177 --> 00:35:47.072
Señorita Banxia,

00:35:48.097 --> 00:35:49.258
