00:36:05.792 --> 00:36:06.698
Dejé esto aquí.

00:36:06.698 --> 00:36:07.584
Jinrong.

00:36:11.338 --> 00:36:12.224
Te ves linda.

00:36:13.017 --> 00:36:15.177
